description:
Rewrapped - Season 1, Episode 9




Now Krimpet! Krimpet Good!

In this episode of Rewrapped, contestants must take on the spongy and sweet icing goodness of the Tastykake Butterscotch Krimpet. During the Recreate Challenge, one contestant runs into a "sticky" problem with the icing. When the competitors move on to the Innovate Challenge, will one contestant's Butterscotch Krimpet Chicken and Waffles idea pan out? You'll have to tune in to Rewrapped to find out!




Original Air Date: 09-Jun-2014
